        <p>
            Remember to write down the benefits of your identity before moving on to the next step of character creation. The bonus skill points generated during this 
            step will be allocated during the next step.
        </p>

        <div class="subCard">
            <h3><em>Optional</em></h3>
            <p>
                Don’t be afraid to come up with your own identity if none of the listed ones work for your character idea. Try to follow the guideline of;

                <ul>
                    <li>5 points between up to 2 attributes</li>
                    <li>Can remove 1 point to add an item</li>
                    <li>Can remove 1 to 2 points to add a feature</li>
                </ul>

                If you've got an idea that you think would fit well with the default game, sent me an email at daniel.allred@towerofillusion.com!
            </p>
        </div>
